These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
City: new-york, berlin, nizza, boston
4 different pets are kept: turtle, lizard, rat, hedgehog
1. the person traveling to berlin is between the person traveling to new-york and the owner of the lizard##2
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
3. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to new-york##7
4. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| City   | nizza | boston       | berlin | new-york        |
| Pet      | rat  | lizard | hedgehog        | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, asparagus, mango, avocado
House: cottage, palace, modern, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is somewhere between the modern house and the person eating mango##7
2. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
3. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
4. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
5. the townhouse house is between the modern house and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Food     | mango | asparagus       | avocado         | pumpkin     |
| House   | palace   | townhouse | modern | cottage |

