.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, pakistani, thai
City: paris, boston, venice, new-york
1. the malaysian is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to paris##7
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the thai##1
4. the person traveling to paris is somewhere between the person traveling to new-york and the turkish##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | turkish | thai | pakistani | malaysian  |
| City   | venice | paris  | new-york   | boston |

