.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, airplane, ship
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, old-henry, swisher, fonseca
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the old-henry-smoker and the person driving the ship##7
3. the person driving the airplane is the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Transport   | skateboard | scooter | ship       | airplane |
| Cigar   | old-henry      | alhambra   | swisher | fonseca  |

