.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, soy-milk, tea
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, fish, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking almond-milk##7
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
6. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | almond-milk   | tea | iced-tea |
| Pet   | hamster      | goat | turtle      | fish |

