.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, banana, plum, apricot
4 different games are played: scrabble, go, billiard, chess
1. the person eating plum is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing billiard is the person eating apricot##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating plum##1
5. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
6. the person playing chess is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the person playing go##7
7. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food      | banana | grapefruit      | plum | apricot     |
| Game   | scrabble    | chess | go   | billiard |

