.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, june, march
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, azalea, zinnia, daisy
1. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in june##7
5. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday          | march    | september   | october | june  |
| Flower   | lily | zinnia | daisy    | azalea |

