.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, go, billiard
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, firefighter, project-manager, scientist
1. the person playing scrabble is not the scientist##6
2. the project-manager is on the left or right of the scientist##3
3. the person playing billiard is the project-manager##1
4. the person playing go is somewhere between the person playing billiard and the person playing monopoly##7
5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the scientist is on the right of the project-manager##1
7. the scientist is on the left of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | billiard | go | scrabble | monopoly |
| Job           | project-manager   | scientist    | fisherman       | firefighter  |

