3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person eating nectarine and the person driving the tram##7
6. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5

.:: Answer ::.
