1. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person drinking milk##7
2. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
3. the person drinking soy-milk is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
4. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
5. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Sport   | sailing | basketball | parkour | badminton |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk   | milk  | iced-tea      |

