4. the engineer is on the left of the social-worker##1
5. the social-worker is between the manager and the person drinking coffee##2
6. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the manager##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Job   | engineer | social-worker | manager | mechanic   |
| Beverage   | coffee    | 7up      | milk      | mirinda |

