.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, mango, grapes, cranberry
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, tulip, poppy, zinnia
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person eating onion##1
2. the person eating cranberry is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growspoppy is the person eating grapes##1
4. the person eating grapes is not the person who growstulip##6
5. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
6. the person who growstulip is somewhere between the person who growsaconite and the person eating grapes##7
7. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food       | cranberry | onion | mango | grapes |
| Flower   | aconite   | zinnia      | tulip        | poppy  |

