.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, ivory, grey, green
City: berlin, marseilles, hamburg, liverpool
1. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere between the person who likes green and the person traveling to hamburg##7
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
4. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
6. the person who likes black is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
7. the person who likes ivory is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Color      | black   | grey | ivory | green   |
| City   | berlin | hamburg   | liverpool | marseilles |

