4 different games are played: backgammon, go, bridge, monopoly
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person playing backgammon##7
5. the person playing go is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Hobby           | puzzles | chess | video-games | drawing  |
| Game   | backgammon     | go   | bridge    | monopoly |

