4. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the baccarat-smoker##5
5. the wooden house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
