.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, snowboarding, handball
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, funk, disco, electronic
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
2. the fan electronic is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the fan rock##5
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
5. the fan electronic is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
6. the fan funk is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is snowboarding##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Sport   | handball | snowboarding | skateboarding      | weightlifting |
| Music-Genre     | electronic  | disco  | funk | rock   |

