.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, techno, reggae, folk
4 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, canasta, domino
1. the fan reggae is somewhere between the person playing chess and the fan techno##7
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the fan folk is on the left of the fan salsa##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the fan reggae##5
5. the fan reggae is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Music-Genre         | techno    | reggae | folk     | salsa |
| Game   | canasta | domino  | mah-jongg | chess |

 